        <item>
            <title>全新平治 EQV 七座電動 MPV 登場，智能科技與豪華舒適兼備</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/16/mercedesbenz-eqv-mpv/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mercedesbenz-eqv-mpv</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/16/mercedesbenz-eqv-mpv/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 06:00:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[bev]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[eqv]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes-Benz]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[七人車]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電動車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281274</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>平治（Mercedes-Benz）今日於中環發佈全新的純電動 MPV 七人車 EQV，結合時尚設計與智能科技，為家庭、商務人士及休閒用家提供更舒適和便捷的駕駛體驗。新款 EQV 採用嶄新設計語言並加入更多科技元素，為家庭用戶、VIP 及商務人士提供卓越的乘駕體驗。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281280" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115546-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115546-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115546.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>外觀設計煥然一新，時尚與動感並重</strong></p><p>全新 EQV 的外觀更具現代感，車頭配備引人注目的鍍鉻鬼面罩及動感十足的保險桿及 LED 燈帶，大大提升科技感。MULTIBEAM LED 頭燈支援高光束輔助功能，根據路面情況自動調節燈光，提升夜間行車安全。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_122858-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_122858-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_122858.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外，新 EQV 車尾設計亦有所升級，全新 LED 燈組提升辨識度，鍍鉻裝飾條上印有 Mercedes-Benz 字樣，配合線條硬朗的擾流板，展現獨特的平治風格。全新 EQV 更推出 hightech silver metallic、kalahari gold metallic、alpine grey 和 vintage blue 四種新車色，合共 12 款顏色選擇，迎合不同用家口味。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_120020-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_120020-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_120020.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>數碼化車廂，奢華與舒適結合</strong></p><p>車廂設計以數碼化為核心，儀錶板搭載兩個 12.3 吋高解像度顯示屏，提供清晰直接的資訊顯示。全新設計的冷氣出風口及觸控識別軚盤，進一步提升科技感。中央控制枱配備無線充電功能，方便用家為智能手機充電。另外，車廂提供 64 種顏色 LED 氣氛燈，用家可按個人喜好調整車內燈光營造獨特氛圍。標配雙趟門設計方便乘客進出車廂，無論日常或商務用途都更便捷。全新 EQV 可容納最多 7 人，客戶可以選擇不同座椅配備包括躺椅式長椅和豪華座椅，可升級的座椅設有傾斜功能、背部按摩、空調、頭部、腿部和腳部支撐，為乘客帶來舒適享受。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281309" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115705-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115705-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115705.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_122757-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_122757-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_122757.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115734-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115734-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115734.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可配備的座椅設有傾斜功能、背部按摩、空調、頭部、腿部和腳部支撐，乘客可以選擇三個按摩級別和三個空調級別。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115758-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115758-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115758.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 中排配備兩個無線充電的感應充電面板，前方兩個 USB-C 埠和兩個隱藏式杯架。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281285" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115751-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115751-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115751.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>新一代 MBUX 智能系統，互動體驗全面升級</strong></p><p>全新 EQV 配備升級版 MBUX 多媒體系統，支援語音助手「你好，平治」，用家可透過廣東話語音、觸控屏幕或軚盤按鈕輕鬆操作。新車首次加入 ENERGIZING 舒適控制模式及 AR 擴增實境導航，讓駕駛過程更輕鬆便捷。此外，透過支援廣東話語音識辨功能的新一代 MBUX，全新 EQV 融入了智能導航系統，具備主動續航距離管理和雲端服務及應用程式，讓駕駛更加輕鬆和安全。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281283" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115914-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115914-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115914.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新的賴向儀錶板配備兩個 12.3 吋顯示屏，解像度為 1,920 x 720 像素。儀表和中央顯示屏在一個玻璃罩下的排列，營造出現代平板電視的效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115516-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115516-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115516.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>安全系統升級，智能輔助更安心</strong></p><p>EQV 的安全系統得到進一步強化，標配主動式剎車輔助系統、盲點輔助及車道保持輔助等。MULTIBEAM LED 頭燈首次引入 Highbeam Assist PLUS 功能，84 顆可獨立控制的 LED 能自動根據交通情況調整光束，避免影響其他駕駛者。此外，泊車套裝提供 3D 立體 360 度鏡頭及拖車輔助功能，泊車及拖車操作更加安全。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281304" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115600-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115600-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_115600.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1281303" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_120037-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_120037-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241213_120037.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>高容量鋰電池，續航力達 365 公里</strong></p><p>全新 EQV 採用 90 kWh 鋰電池，續航里程最高可達 365 公里（WLTP 標準）。新車支援最高 110 kW DC 直流快充，只需約 40 分鐘就能將電量從 10% 充至 80%。</p><h3>Mercedes Benz EQV 規格表</h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1281276 alignleft" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/eqv_spec-694x540.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="540" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/eqv_spec-694x540.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/eqv_spec.jpg 747w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
